# CardCast optional API keys
#
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in any keys you have. The .env file is
# gitignored and never committed. All keys are OPTIONAL: CardCast works fully
# without them (anonymous requests). Real environment variables take priority
# over this file.
#
# Resolution priority for every key: process.env > config.local.json > none.

# Pokemon TCG (https://pokemontcg.io) - optional.
# Without a key, requests are anonymous and subject to lower rate limits.
# With a key it is sent as the X-Api-Key header to api.pokemontcg.io.
POKEMONTCG_API_KEY=
